Class AbstractRoutine<IN,OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.core.routine.TemplateRoutine<IN,OUT>
      • com.github.dm.jrt.core.AbstractRoutine<IN,OUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the input data type.
    OUT - the output data type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Routine<IN,OUT>

    public abstract class AbstractRoutine<IN,OUT>
extends TemplateRoutine<IN,OUT>
    Basic abstract implementation of a routine.

    This class provides a default implementation of all the routine features, like invocation modes and recycling of invocation objects.
    The inheriting class just needs to create invocation objects when required.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 09/07/2014.
